snippet.title: Roblox Aquaman Event Feat. Jason Momoa and Amber Heard
snippet.description:
The wrath of the Seven Seas is coming to the surface. Will you unite these two worlds and take your rightful throne? Face ancient trials and earn exclusive virtual prizes in our new event sponsored by #Aquaman, in theaters December 21. https://goo.gl/zL3Wop 


Want to see more Roblox content? SUBSCRIBE to our channel! https://www.youtube.com/user/roblox?sub_confirmation=1
 
Roblox’s Imagination Platform is ushering in the next generation of entertainment, enabling kids of all ages to imagine, create, and play together in immersive 3D worlds. Powered by a global community of millions of developers and creators, Roblox allows anyone to build, publish, and monetize any experience imaginable. Roblox is freely available on all modern smartphones, tablets, computers, Xbox One, Oculus Rift, and HTC Vive.
